rs\" href=\"/admin\">★ Super Admin</a><a class=\"hover:text-cyan-600 text-slate-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/dashboard\">Tenant Admin</a><a class=\"hover:text-cyan-600 text-cyan-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/builder\">✎ Visual Builder</a><a class=\"hover:text-cyan-600 text-slate-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/pos\">POS Caja</a><a class=\"hover:text-cyan-600 text-slate-600 transition-colors underline decoration-cyan-400\" href=\"/inicio\">Ver Tienda</a><a class=\"hover:text-cyan-600 text-slate-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/login\">Login/Registro</a></div><div class=\"hidden lg:block text-slate-400 font-mono text-[10px]\">Status: <span class=\"text-green-600 font-bold\">Online</span></div></nav><div class=\"w-full min-h-[calc(100vh-3rem)] bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-[#f0f9fb] to-white text-slate-800 flex flex-col justify-between\"><header class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-16 text-center flex flex-col items-center gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 bg-celeste-claro/30 text-primary-celeste rounded-full text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest animate-pulse border border-[#bce6ed]/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-3.5 h-3.5\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg> Portal de Infraestructura SaaS</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-none max-w-4xl\">Dominios, Servidores Dedicados y Suscripciones SaaS Bajo Control</h1><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">NRAM360 te provee de dominios con SSL administrado y VPS en la nube autogestionados para desplegar instantáneamente tu Academia LMS o POS de Ventas.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-4\"><a href=\"#suscripciones\" class=\"px-8 py-4 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full font-bold shadow-xl hover:bg-primary-celeste hover:text-slate-950 transition-all hover:scale-105 duration-300\">Ver Planes de Suscripción</a><a class=\"px-8 py-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-900 rounded-full font-bold shadow hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all hover:scale-105 duration-300 flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/admin\">Consola Super Admin <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-primary-celeste\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></header><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-10\"><div class=\"bg-white/80 backdrop-blur border border-celeste-claro/50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-28 h-28 bg-primary-celeste/10 rounded-full blur-2xl\"></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-6 h-6 text-primary-celeste animate-bounce\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg> Registrar tu Dominio o Subdominio</h3><p class=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1\">Verifica la disponibilidad de tu dirección comercial. El Super Admin autogestiona el ruteo DNS CNAME.</p></div><form class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3\"><div class=\"flex-grow flex border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-primary-celeste transition-all bg-white\"><span class=\"flex items-center pl-4 text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search w-4 h-4\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><path d=\"m21 21-4.3-4.3\"></path></svg></span><input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"ej. miacademiaoventas\" class=\"w-full px-3 py-3.5 bg-transparent border-0 text-slate-800 focus:ring-0 text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none font-bold\" value=\"\"/></div><select class=\"px-4 py-3.5 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-celeste text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 outline-none\"><option value=\".nram360.com\" selected=\"\">.nram360.com (Subdominio)</option><option value=\".com\">.com (Dominio Propio)</option><option value=\".net\">.net (Dominio Propio)</option></select><button type=\"submit\" class=\"px-8 py-3.5 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-primary-celeste hover:text-slate-950 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase\">Buscar</button></form></div></section><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 items-center\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-6\"><div><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-celeste font-black block\">Infraestructura Dedicada</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mt-1\">Hosting Servidores Cloud VPS</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed\">Asigna recursos de hosting dedicados a tus inquilinos de acuerdo a su tráfico. Configuración auto-escalable en Kubernetes gestionada por el Super Admin.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center text-xs font-bold text-slate-700\"><span>Seleccionar Recursos Cloud</span><span class=\"text-primary-celeste font-black\">Cloud VPS Dedicado Pro</span></div><input type=\"range\" min=\"1\" max=\"3\" step=\"1\" class=\"w-full accent-primary-celeste cursor-pointer h-2 bg-slate-200 rounded-lg appearance-none\" value=\"2\"/><div class=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 px-1\"><span>Básico</span><span>Pro Dedicado</span><span>Enterprise</span></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-3 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-800\"><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] bg-slate-800 text-primary-celeste px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-mono font-bold border border-slate-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity w-3 h-3 animate-pulse text-green-500\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg> STATUS: ACTIVE</div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-4\"><div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-black\">Plan Cloud Server</span><h4 class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-white mt-0.5\">Cloud VPS Dedicado Pro</h4></div><div class=\"text-right\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-black block\">Costo mensual</span><span class=\"text-xl font-black text-primary-celeste\">$15.00/mes</span></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-xs font-mono\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-800\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><rect width=\"16\" height=\"16\" x=\"4\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect width=\"6\" height=\"6\" x=\"9\" y=\"9\" rx=\"1\"></rect><path d=\"M15 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M15 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M9 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 20v2\"></path></svg><div><span class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 block\">Procesador</span><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">2 vCPU Dedicados Xeon</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-800\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-database w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><ellipse cx=\"12\" cy=\"5\" rx=\"9\" ry=\"3\"></ellipse><path d=\"M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5\"></path><path d=\"M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12\"></path></svg><div><span class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 block\">Memoria RAM</span><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">4 GB DDR4 RAM</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-800\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-server w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"14\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg><div><span class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 block\">Almacenamiento</span><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">80 GB SSD NVMe</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 p-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-800\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg><div><span class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 block\">Ancho de Banda</span><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">5 TB Ancho de Banda</span></div></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 text-[10px]\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-ping\"></span><span class=\"text-slate-400 font-semibold\">Latencia Edge:</span><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">12ms promedio</span></div><span class=\"text-primary-celeste font-bold italic\">Ideal para: <!-- -->Pro Plan, academias medianas y POS sincronizados</span></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"suscripciones\" class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-celeste font-black block\">Planes Flexibles</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 mt-1\">Planes de Suscripción SaaS</h2><p class=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2 max-w-xl mx-auto\">Habilita módulos específicos (Academia LMS, POS de Ventas o Ecommerce) de acuerdo a tu modelo de negocio comercial.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"p-6 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-md flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-slate-300 transition-all\"><div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-black tracking-widest block\">Pequeños Negocios</span><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mt-0.5\">Starter Plan</h4><span class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mt-3 block\">$19.00 <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold\">/ mes</span></span><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 mt-6 text-xs text-slate-600\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Constructor Visual (4 capas)</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Módulo POS de Ventas Offline</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-slate-300 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Aula LMS Cursos (No incluido)</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Subdominio .nram360.com gratis</li></ul></div><a class=\"w-full py-3 text-center bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 font-bold rounded-xl mt-8 text-xs transition-colors block\" href=\"/login?register=true&amp;plan=Starter\">Contratar Starter</a></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-3xl bg-white border-2 border-primary-celeste shadow-xl flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-celeste text-slate-950 font-black text-[9px] uppercase px-3 py-1.5 rounded-bl-xl shadow\">Recomendado</div><div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-primary-celeste uppercase font-black tracking-widest block\">Crecimiento rápido</span><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mt-0.5\">Pro Plan</h4><span class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mt-3 block\">$49.00 <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold\">/ mes</span></span><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 mt-6 text-xs text-slate-600\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Constructor Visual (4 capas)</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Módulo POS de Ventas Offline</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chec